==English==

===Noun===
'''engineer'''
# A person who is [[qualified]] or [[professionally]] [[engaged]] in any [[branch]] of [[engineering]].
# (''formerly'') A person who [[operate]]s an [[engine]] (such as a [[locomotive]]).
# A person given a [[problem]] finds a [[solution]].

